name: VA-East Side Story Limited Box Set Edition Vol. 1 - 12
description:
If you are a true lover of oldies to cruise by, then this set is it. The set is well thought out and features the more popular songs which people can remember. Know wondering if you know that song here's an interesting addition to this set from the albums/cassettes is that some of the more current, 1980's, songs have been added onto each CD. This should help some of those newcomers to the scene feel comfortable about identifying with their cruiser days.
